OL,4,CCouncillors call for online meetings to
OL,5,Ccontinue post-pandemic
OL,6, Councillors are calling for a law in
OL,7, the Queen's Speech to allow them to
OL,8, continue online meetings and "serve the
OL,9, best interests of our people".
OL,11,FLocal authorities adjusted like most
OL,12,Forganisations during lockdown by moving
OL,13,Ftheir gatherings onto apps like Zoom.
OL,15,FBut the emergency legislation allowing
OL,16,Fthe move ran out on 6 May, leaving
OL,17,Fcouncils with Covid safety concerns.
OL,19,FThe government has launched a
OL,20,Fconsultation on remote meetings to look
OL,21,Fat potential "next steps".
